query:
SELECT
                token_id,
                contract_index,
                contract_sub_index,
                balance as raw_balance,
                account_index as account_id
            FROM account_tokens
            WHERE account_tokens.contract_index = $1 AND account_tokens.contract_sub_index = $2 AND account_tokens.token_id = $3 AND account_tokens.index_per_token >= $4
            LIMIT $5
